  "title": "Class 3 / Class 4 Delivery Driver - 5 Days, Multiple Location Available",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibility :</strong></p><ul><li>Pick up, transport, and deliver goods to assigned destinations in a timely and safe manner</li><li>Ensure proper handling, loading, and unloading of goods to prevent damage</li><li>Maintain delivery vehicle cleanliness and ensure it is in good working condition</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement :</strong></p><ul><li>Possess a valid Class 3 or Class 4 Singapore driving license</li><li>Entry Level is welcome to apply. Training will be provided</li><li>Delivery Attendant positions are also available</li><li>Physically fit and able to carry loads</li><li>Class 4 driver will operate 24ft truck</li><li>Class 3 driver will operate Van or 10ft or 14ft Truck</li><li>Working days: 5.5 days</li><li>Cargo (Ranging form home Appliance, Palletized, FMCG or parcels)</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Benefit :</strong></p><ul><li>Vehicle can be driven home</li><li>Attractive bonus scheme (Performance Bonus and/or AWS)</li><li>Medical benefits provided</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
